The paper discusses the development of algorithms for autonomous driving using computer vision techniques, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques for multi-task learning and sensor fusion, which could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of semantic segmentation for understanding objects, which could fall under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL).
